  "slug": "craft-6-stairs-not-4",
  "title": "Craft 6 Stairs Instead of 4",
  "description": "Get the same number of stairs from crafting as you would from using a stonecutter",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wLbV6lc.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/craft-6-stairs-not-4\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/477004?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/craft-6-stairs-not-4\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/craft-6-stairs-not-4?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Crafting stairs in the crafting table will yield six stairs instead of four to match the number of stairs you would get using a stonecutter.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CuHq65H.png\"/></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/sixstairs.json</code> in your profile folder. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>stairAmount</b> - determines how many stairs you get from crafting</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>blockStairsList</b> - list of blocks and the corresponding stairs you can craft from them</p></center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://url-shortener.curseforge.com/uBxl2\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y3LiTfU.png\"/></a></p>",
